snippet.title: Phantom Hellcat - Gameaplay Presentation - Future Games Show Gamescom 2022
snippet.description: Phantom Hellcat is a slasher platformer from Ironbird Creations, and the developers presented an in-depth look at the game during the Future Games Show at Gamescom 2022. Phantom Hellcat is coming soon to PC, PlayStation and Xbox
